17
00:07:18,781 --> 00:07:47,502
We also permit all dumpsters, permanent dumpsters and temporary dumpsters. The ordinance requires permanent dumpsters submit IPMs to the Board of Health as well, prior to their permanent renewal. And again, that's an effort to make sure that dumpsters are maintained appropriately, that they're clean, that they're plugged, that they're also that they have an IPM plan in place to ensure that the rodents are kept at bay.

18
00:07:48,481 --> 00:08:08,191
